    {
        "content": "<p>This is the biggest diagram I've encountered so far<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/rwbarton/lean-homotopy-theory/blob/lean-3.4.2/src/homotopy_theory/formal/cofibrations/gluing.lean#L18\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/rwbarton/lean-homotopy-theory/blob/lean-3.4.2/src/homotopy_theory/formal/cofibrations/gluing.lean#L18\">https://github.com/rwbarton/lean-homotopy-theory/blob/lean-3.4.2/src/homotopy_theory/formal/cofibrations/gluing.lean#L18</a></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kn\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÇ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÅ‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÉ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÇ‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÑ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÉ‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÑ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">po_f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Is_pushout</span> <span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÅ‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÇ‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"n\">f‚ÇÉ‚ÇÑ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÇ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÅ‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÉ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÇ‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÑ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÉ‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÑ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">po_g</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Is_pushout</span> <span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÅ‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÇ‚ÇÑ</span> <span class=\"n\">g‚ÇÉ‚ÇÑ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÅ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÇ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÇ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÉ</span> <span class=\"err\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b‚ÇÉ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- u‚ÇÑ will be the induced map of pushouts</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ha‚ÇÅ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">cofibrant</span> <span class=\"n\">a‚ÇÅ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n